data.description: Unlock the potential of your forever home. This well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick residence, with a new roof (2022), mature trees, fully fenced backyard, A/C unit that is approximately 10 years old. This home offers an ideal canvas for your personal touch and make it truly your own. Cozy up by the fireplace and enjoy the view into your secluded backyard that is shadowed by trees. Don't forget about the efficiency apartment and the income potential it provides. This home is a must see.
